import React, { useState } from 'react';
import {
  View,
  Text,
  TextInput,
  TouchableOpacity,
  StyleSheet,
  SafeAreaView,
  ScrollView,
  Alert,
} from 'react-native';
import { LinearGradient } from 'expo-linear-gradient';
import { StatusBar } from 'expo-status-bar';

export default function App() {
  const [currentScreen, setCurrentScreen] = useState('login');
  const [email, setEmail] = useState('');
  const [password, setPassword] = useState('');
  const [user, setUser] = useState(null);

  const handleLogin = () => {
    if (!email || !password) {
      Alert.alert('Error', 'Please fill in all fields');
      return;
    }
    setUser({ name: 'Test User', email });
    setCurrentScreen('dashboard');
  };

  const handleLogout = () => {
    setUser(null);
    setCurrentScreen('login');
    setEmail('');
    setPassword('');
  };

  if (currentScreen === 'login') {
    return (
      <SafeAreaView style={styles.container}>
        <LinearGradient colors={['#2563EB', '#1E40AF']} style={styles.gradient}>
          <ScrollView contentContainerStyle={styles.scrollContent}>
            <View style={styles.logoContainer}>
              <View style={styles.logo}>
                <Text style={styles.logoText}>üèõÔ∏è</Text>
              </View>
              <Text style={styles.title}>Gujarat Portal</Text>
              <Text style={styles.subtitle}>Mobile App v2.0</Text>
            </View>

            <View style={styles.card}>
              <Text style={styles.cardTitle}>Welcome Back</Text>
              <Text style={styles.cardSubtitle}>Sign in to continue</Text>

              <View style={styles.inputContainer}>
                <Text style={styles.label}>Email</Text>
                <TextInput
                  style={styles.input}
                  placeholder="Enter your email"
                  value={email}
                  onChangeText={setEmail}
                  keyboardType="email-address"
                  autoCapitalize="none"
                />
              </View>

              <View style={styles.inputContainer}>
                <Text style={styles.label}>Password</Text>
                <TextInput
                  style={styles.input}
                  placeholder="Enter your password"
                  value={password}
                  onChangeText={setPassword}
                  secureTextEntry
                />
              </View>

              <TouchableOpacity onPress={handleLogin}>
                <LinearGradient colors={['#2563EB', '#1D4ED8']} style={styles.button}>
                  <Text style={styles.buttonText}>Sign In ‚Üí</Text>
                </LinearGradient>
              </TouchableOpacity>

              <View style={styles.testInfo}>
                <Text style={styles.testInfoText}>üí° Test: Use any email and password</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
          </ScrollView>
        </LinearGradient>
        <StatusBar style="light" />
      </SafeAreaView>
    );
  }

  return (
    <SafeAreaView style={styles.container}>
      <ScrollView>
        <LinearGradient colors={['#2563EB', '#1D4ED8']} style={styles.header}>
          <View style={styles.headerContent}>
            <View>
              <Text style={styles.welcomeText}>Welcome Back</Text>
              <Text style={styles.userName}>{user?.name || 'User'}</Text>
              <Text style={styles.userEmail}>{user?.email}</Text>
            </View>
            <TouchableOpacity onPress={handleLogout} style={styles.logoutButton}>
              <Text style={styles.logoutText}>Logout</Text>
            </TouchableOpacity>
          </View>
        </LinearGradient>

        <View style={styles.statsContainer}>
          {[
            { label: 'Applications', value: '5', icon: 'üìä' },
            { label: 'Pending', value: '2', icon: '‚è≥' },
            { label: 'Completed', value: '3', icon: '‚úÖ' },
          ].map((stat, index) => (
            <View key={index} style={styles.statCard}>
              <Text style={styles.statIcon}>{stat.icon}</Text>
              <Text style={styles.statValue}>{stat.value}</Text>
              <Text style={styles.statLabel}>{stat.label}</Text>
            </View>
          ))}
        </View>

        <View style={styles.section}>
          <Text style={styles.sectionTitle}>Explore Services</Text>
          {[
            { title: 'Utility Services', desc: 'Electricity, Gas, Water', icon: '‚ö°', color: ['#F59E0B', '#D97706'] },
            { title: 'Company Formation', desc: 'GST, TAN, PAN', icon: 'üíº', color: ['#3B82F6', '#2563EB'] },
            { title: 'Government Grants', desc: 'Startup, MSME', icon: 'üéÅ', color: ['#10B981', '#059669'] },
          ].map((service, index) => (
            <TouchableOpacity key={index}>
              <LinearGradient colors={service.color} style={styles.serviceCard}>
                <View style={styles.serviceIconContainer}>
                  <Text style={styles.serviceIcon}>{service.icon}</Text>
                </View>
                <View style={styles.serviceContent}>
                  <Text style={styles.serviceTitle}>{service.title}</Text>
                  <Text style={styles.serviceDesc}>{service.desc}</Text>
                </View>
                <Text style={styles.serviceArrow}>‚Üí</Text>
              </LinearGradient>
            </TouchableOpacity>
          ))}
        </View>

        <View style={styles.successBanner}>
          <Text style={styles.successIcon}>üéâ</Text>
          <View>
            <Text style={styles.successTitle}>App is Working!</Text>
            <Text style={styles.successText}>All features functional</Text>
          </View>
        </View>
      </ScrollView>
      <StatusBar style="light" />
    </SafeAreaView>
  );
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: { flex: 1, backgroundColor: '#F8FAFC' },
  gradient: { flex: 1 },
  scrollContent: { flexGrow: 1, padding: 24, paddingTop: 60 },
  logoContainer: { alignItems: 'center', marginBottom: 40 },
  logo: { width: 80, height: 80, borderRadius: 20, backgroundColor: '#FFFFFF', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', marginBottom: 16 },
  logoText: { fontSize: 40 },
  title: { fontSize: 28, fontWeight: '800', color: '#FFFFFF', marginBottom: 4 },
  subtitle: { fontSize: 16, color: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8)' },
  card: { backgroundColor: '#FFFFFF', borderRadius: 24, padding: 24 },
  cardTitle: { fontSize: 24, fontWeight: '700', color: '#1E293B', marginBottom: 4 },
  cardSubtitle: { fontSize: 14, color: '#64748B', marginBottom: 24 },
  inputContainer: { marginBottom: 16 },
  label: { fontSize: 14, fontWeight: '600', color: '#334155', marginBottom: 8 },
  input: { height: 50, backgroundColor: '#F8FAFC', borderRadius: 12, paddingHorizontal: 16, fontSize: 16, borderWidth: 2, borderColor: '#E2E8F0' },
  button: { height: 50, borderRadius: 12, alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', marginTop: 8 },
  buttonText: { fontSize: 16, fontWeight: '700', color: '#FFFFFF' },
  testInfo: { marginTop: 16, padding: 12, backgroundColor: '#DBEAFE', borderRadius: 12 },
  testInfoText: { fontSize: 12, color: '#1E40AF', textAlign: 'center', fontWeight: '600' },
  header: { padding: 24, paddingTop: 40, borderBottomLeftRadius: 24, borderBottomRightRadius: 24 },
  headerContent: { flexDirection: 'row', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center' },
  welcomeText: { fontSize: 14, color: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8)', fontWeight: '600' },
  userName: { fontSize: 24, fontWeight: '700', color: '#FFFFFF', marginTop: 4 },
  userEmail: { fontSize: 12, color: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)', marginTop: 2 },
  logoutButton: { backgroundColor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2)', paddingHorizontal: 16, paddingVertical: 8, borderRadius: 12 },
  logoutText: { color: '#FFFFFF', fontWeight: '600' },
  statsContainer: { flexDirection: 'row', padding: 20, gap: 12 },
  statCard: { flex: 1, backgroundColor: '#FFFFFF', borderRadius: 16, padding: 16, alignItems: 'center' },
  statIcon: { fontSize: 24, marginBottom: 8 },
  statValue: { fontSize: 24, fontWeight: '700', color: '#1E293B', marginBottom: 4 },
  statLabel: { fontSize: 12, color: '#64748B', fontWeight: '600' },
  section: { padding: 20 },
  sectionTitle: { fontSize: 20, fontWeight: '700', color: '#1E293B', marginBottom: 16 },
  serviceCard: { flexDirection: 'row', alignItems: 'center', borderRadius: 16, padding: 16, marginBottom: 12 },
  serviceIconContainer: { width: 48, height: 48, borderRadius: 12, backgroundColor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3)', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', marginRight: 12 },
  serviceIcon: { fontSize: 28 },
  serviceContent: { flex: 1 },
  serviceTitle: { fontSize: 16, fontWeight: '700', color: '#FFFFFF', marginBottom: 2 },
  serviceDesc: { fontSize: 12, color: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9)' },
  serviceArrow: { fontSize: 24, color: '#FFFFFF', fontWeight: '700' },
  successBanner: { margin: 20, padding: 20, backgroundColor: '#D1FAE5', borderRadius: 16, flexDirection: 'row', alignItems: 'center' },
  successIcon: { fontSize: 32, marginRight: 12 },
  successTitle: { fontSize: 16, fontWeight: '700', color: '#065F46', marginBottom: 2 },
  successText: { fontSize: 13, fontWeight: '500', color: '#047857' },
});
